	charset=Windows-1252

Hi there

Thank you for contacting Tower Insurance. This is an auto reply to confirm =
we=92ve received your email and your request will be processed. We=92ll be =
back in touch as soon as possible.

If your query is urgent please phone your Claims Manager. If you have recen=
tly lodged your claim, you will receive their details within 24 working hou=
rs.

Did you know that some of our most common queries can be solved 24/7 throug=
h our new self-service portal My Tower?

With My Tower, customers with Tower house, contents, and car policies can m=
anage their insurance online. No more waiting to speak to a person!

  *   Make a payment or check when your next payment is due
  *   View your policy details, upcoming renewals and all your policy docum=
ents
  *   Change your address, sum insured, excess, or interested party
  *   Update or change your bank account and credit card
  *   Make a claim =96 it=92s easier than you might think!

To find out whether My Tower is available for you, register here<https://my=
.tower.co.nz/auth/login>.

 Kind regards,

The team at Tower

[A blue square with white text  Description automatically generated]
[Text  Description automatically generated with low confidence]

Fair Insurance Code
Tower is a member of the Insurance Council of New Zealand (ICNZ).
We abide by the ICNZ Fair Insurance Code<https://www.icnz.org.nz/fair-insur=
ance-code/>.



________________________________

The information contained in this email message is confidential and may be =
legally privileged. If you are not the intended recipient, please note that=
 any use, dissemination, distribution, or reproduction of this message in a=
ny form whatsoever, is strictly prohibited. If you received this email in e=
rror, please notify me by return email, delete your copy, and accept my apo=
logies for any inconvenience caused. Please note that your receipt of this =
email from a Tower email address does not constitute our consent for you to=
 send any other electronic information to Tower by return, unless specifica=
lly stated otherwise.

--_000_02914aa33e134a05860e39fb2dc5c2e0SYBP282MB0473AUSP282PRO_
