<body lang=3D"EN-US" link=3D"#0563C1" vlink=3D"#954F72" style=3D"word-wrap:=
break-word">
<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p><span lang=3D"EN-NZ" style=3D"font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans=
-serif">Hi there</span><span lang=3D"EN-NZ"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p><span lang=3D"EN-NZ" style=3D"font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans=
-serif">Thank you for contacting Tower Insurance. This is an auto reply to =
confirm we=92ve received your email and your request will be processed. We=
=92ll be back in touch as soon as possible.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p><span lang=3D"EN-NZ" style=3D"font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans=
-serif">If your query is urgent please phone your Claims Manager. If you ha=
ve recently lodged your claim, you will receive their details within 24 wor=
king hours.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p><span lang=3D"EN-NZ" style=3D"font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans=
-serif">Did you know that some of our most common queries can be solved 24/=
7 through our new self-service portal My Tower?
</span><span lang=3D"EN-NZ"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p><span lang=3D"EN-NZ" style=3D"font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans=
-serif">With My Tower, customers with Tower house, contents, and car polici=
es can manage their insurance online. No more waiting to speak to a person!
</span><span lang=3D"EN-NZ"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-=
alt:auto;margin-left:-15.75pt;line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3">
<span lang=3D"EN-NZ" style=3D"font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-se=
rif">Make a payment or check when your next payment is due
</span><span lang=3D"EN-NZ"><o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" =
style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;margin-left:-15=
.75pt;line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3">
<span lang=3D"EN-NZ" style=3D"font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-se=
rif">View your policy details, upcoming renewals and all your policy docume=
nts
</span><span lang=3D"EN-NZ"><o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" =
style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;margin-left:-15=
.75pt;line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3">
<span lang=3D"EN-NZ" style=3D"font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-se=
rif">Change your address, sum insured, excess, or interested party
</span><span lang=3D"EN-NZ"><o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" =
style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;margin-left:-15=
.75pt;line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3">
<span lang=3D"EN-NZ" style=3D"font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-se=
rif">Update or change your bank account and credit card
</span><span lang=3D"EN-NZ"><o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" =
style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;margin-left:-15=
.75pt;line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3">
<span lang=3D"EN-NZ" style=3D"font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans-se=
rif">Make a claim =96 it=92s easier than you might think!
</span><span lang=3D"EN-NZ"><o:p></o:p></span></li></ul>
<p><span lang=3D"EN-NZ" style=3D"font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans=
-serif">To find out whether My Tower is available for you, register
<a href=3D"https://my.tower.co.nz/auth/login" title=3D"https://my.tower.co.=
nz/auth/login">
here</a>.</span><span lang=3D"EN-NZ"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p><span lang=3D"EN-NZ" style=3D"font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans=
-serif">&nbsp;Kind regards,
</span><span lang=3D"EN-NZ"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p><span lang=3D"EN-NZ" style=3D"font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;,sans=
-serif">The team at Tower<br>
<br>
